| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2025-7355 — Recovery Inhibition (qilin)"
| comment "Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: 8868dc8d-5e2b-580f-a7ee-ba5c1abee7b5"
